Package com.github.tcn.plexi.settingsManager

Class Settings

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.tcn.plexi.settingsManager.Settings
  • public class Settings
extends java.lang.Object
    The Settings class for Plexi
    This class follows a singleton pattern in an attempt to stop superfluous reloading of the settings text file located in the same folder as the Plexi jar. There is currently NO way to change any of these settings values once they are set.
